thread.title: BRIEF-MSB Financial Corp Posts Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.05

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-MSB Financial Corp Posts Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.05
text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - MSB Financial Corp:
* RELEASES FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR EARNINGS * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.05 * MSB FINANCIAL - ‍TOTAL INTEREST INCOME FOR THREE MONTHS ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2017 INCREASED $1.4 MILLION, OR 36.2%, TO $5.4 MILLION COMPARED TO $3.9 MILLION FOR Q4 OF 2016​
* MSB FINANCIAL - ‍NET INTEREST INCOME FOR THREE MONTHS ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2017 INCREASED $1.0 MILLION TO $4.3 MILLION COMPARED TO SAME THREE MONTH PERIOD IN 2016​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
